# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Troopod Landing Page Personalizer — Environment Config
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# MULTI-PROVIDER STRATEGY (add keys for each to maximize quota):
#
#  Provider     | Best For          | Free Limits          | Get Key At
#  -------------|-------------------|----------------------|----------------------------------
#  Gemini       | Vision (images)   | 15 RPM, 1500/day     | aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#  Groq         | Text (executor)   | 30 RPM, 14400/day    | console.groq.com/keys
#  OpenRouter   | Fallback (text)   | 20 RPM, unlimited*   | openrouter.ai/settings/keys
#
# * OpenRouter :free models have no daily limit but may queue during peak hours
#
# You MUST have at least one of these. Having all three is recommended.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# REQUIRED: Vision tasks (ad image analysis)
# Get free key: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# RECOMMENDED: Text personalization (executor agent uses this first)
# Get free key: https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# RECOMMENDED: Fallback provider (many free models, no daily cap)
# Get free key: https://openrouter.ai/settings/keys
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_openrouter_api_key_here

# Server config
PORT=3001
NODE_ENV=development
